# pptides.com — Full Codebase Context

## What It Is
Arabic RTL SaaS — first comprehensive Arabic peptide guide. 47 peptides (count derived from data), 6 categories, dose calculator, AI coach (MSA), injection tracker, wellness check-in, lab results tracker, side effects log, subscription tiers. Live at https://pptides.com. Repo at ~/Desktop/Projects/REWIRE/peptide-protocols/.

## Stack
React 18 + TypeScript + Vite 7 + Tailwind CSS + Supabase (auth + DB + edge functions) + Stripe + Resend + DeepSeek AI + Vercel. PWA via vite-plugin-pwa. Font: Cairo. Direction: RTL.

## File Map
- `src/lib/` — supabase.ts, utils.ts (cn, arPlural), constants.ts (PRICING with annual, PEPTIDE_COUNT derived from peptides.length, FREQUENCY_LABELS shared constant, FREE_PEPTIDE_IDS, TRIAL_PEPTIDE_IDS, STORAGE_KEYS, SITE_URL), analytics.ts, peptide-labels.ts, markdown.tsx (DOMPurify-sanitized)
- `src/data/` — peptides.ts (47 peptides, 6 categories, 5 stacks, 11 lab tests), dose-presets.ts, interactions.ts, glossary.ts
- `src/contexts/` — AuthContext.tsx (Subscription state machine: none→trial→active→past_due→cancelled→expired, payment polling with specific error messages)
- `src/components/` — Header, Footer, BottomNav (mobile 4-tab nav), ProtectedRoute, TrialBanner (uses AuthContext booleans, sequenced overlays), ProtocolWizard (React Router navigate), PaymentProcessing (React Router navigate), WellnessCheckin, LabResultsTracker, SideEffectLog, ShareableCard, Skeletons (Bone accepts style prop)
- `src/pages/` — 24 pages. Key: Landing (instant render, no auth blocking), Library (diacritics-stripped search), Coach (DOMPurify-sanitized print, MSA system prompt, maxLength=2000), Dashboard (wellness + lab results for paid users), Tracker (CSV injection safe, computeStreak utility, side effects log), Account, DoseCalculator, Admin (server-side auth only, enquiry reply, lang="en"), Pricing (FAQ schema, annual pricing from constants), Logout, Quiz (h1 for SEO)
- `supabase/functions/` — 14 edge functions: stripe-webhook, ai-coach, create-checkout, delete-account, health-check, trial-reminder, cancel-subscription, create-portal-session, inbound-email, admin-stats, admin-actions, send-welcome-email, send-enquiry-reply, verify-stripe (CRON_SECRET)
- `supabase/migrations/` — Security fixes (scoped RLS), email_logs table, cron schedules, schema fixes (reviews columns, enquiries FK)

## Pricing & Auth
Essentials 34 ر.س/mo (296 ر.س/yr), Elite 371 ر.س/mo (2,963 ر.س/yr). SAR currency. 3-day Stripe trial. Supabase Auth (email + Google OAuth). Stripe Checkout + webhooks. Price IDs: STRIPE_PRICE_ESSENTIALS, STRIPE_PRICE_ELITE env vars.

## Source of Truth
- PEPTIDE_COUNT: derived from peptides.length in constants.ts. Edge functions use local constant with source-of-truth comment.
- PRICING: defined in constants.ts with monthly and annual. All UI references use the constant.
- FREQUENCY_LABELS: single definition in constants.ts, imported everywhere.
- SITE_URL: used for all og:image and og:url meta tags.
- Subscription logic: AuthContext provides isPaidSubscriber, isTrial, isProOrTrial. Components use these booleans, not raw status checks.
